Package: ridge
Title: Ridge Regression with Automatic Selection of the Penalty Parameter
Description: Linear and logistic ridge regression functions. Additionally includes special functions for 
            genome-wide single-nucleotide polymorphism data.
Version: 2.2
Date: 2017-02-19
Author: Steffen Moritz, Erika Cule
Maintainer: Steffen Moritz <steffen.moritz10@gmail.com>
Type: Package
